  "texts": [
    "The section explores studies that incorporated time constraints, tardiness objectives, and other time-related considerations.",
    "It also provides insights into the challenges and strategies associated with managing time constraints in MS-RCPSP.",
    "Performance measuresThe MS-RCPSP is known for being a complex problem (NPhard) and its many variants have been extensively studied in the literature.",
    "In essence, towards fulfilling project objectives, the MS-RCPSP requires the scheduling of a series of interdependent tasks in the presence of limited and multi skilled resources, such as labour and equipment.",
    "The selection of appropriate performance measures to evaluate the effectiveness of various scheduling strategies is a crucial aspect of this problem."
  ]
}